<L>__{exterior stratosphere day}
<A>__{the glory of stratospheric dawn. the engines of a silver lockheed u 2f rasp upon the trace oxygen here at 72,500 feet. scattered cloud formations hang over the blue brilliance of sea far, far below. in the haze, the looming edge of land. super: flight g 3101. october 14th, 1962. over cuba. the spy plane's camera doors whine open. the glassy eye of the 36 inch camera focuses. and then with a bangbangbangbang, its high speed motor kicks in, shutter flying.}
